<figcaption><p>Predictors of incident fracture while on treatment.</p></figcaption></figure><figure class="fig xbox font-sm" id="F5"><h3 class="obj_head">FIGURE 5.</h3>
<p class="img-box line-height-none margin-x-neg-2 tablet:margin-x-0 text-center"><a class="tileshop" target="_blank" href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/core/lw/2.0/html/tileshop_pmc/tileshop_pmc_inline.html?title=Click%20on%20image%20to%20zoom&amp;p=PMC3&amp;id=3867340_emss-54710-f0005.jpg"><img class="graphic zoom-in" src="https://cdn.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/blobs/4884/3867340/d4dfb9f590ce/emss-54710-f0005.jpg" loading="lazy" height="437" width="600" alt="FIGURE 5"></a></p>
